{"tid":2079113,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"應唔應該借錢比有正職的細佬進修?","createTime":"2020-06-25T14:27:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T02:16:43.000Z","uid":294147,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0a58ed996e4a71f7917bb635cc0d74dab1fb1b17","tid":2079113,"uid":294147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T14:27:31.000Z","msg":"本人細佬 三大science grad 2up<br />\n畢業頭一年去左做中學的TA，試過報PGDE但唔收<br />\n之後就轉左一兩份工，現在做緊工程公司，聽佢講工作係做電同畫圖<br />\n曾經報過engineering 的 master，都係唔收<br />\n<br />\n而家佢想進修，讀part time degree 或者 去外國讀<br />\n佢話香港無咩part time degree，打算去外國讀，現在問我借錢進修<br />\n我都好想幫佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;但又擔心佢讀完都30歲了，無左好多年工作經驗會好輸蝕<br />\n而且唔知外國讀返黎香港的認受性如何<br />\n<br />\n我查過佢本地能夠入到的應該得polyu speed EE，唔清楚認受性係點<br />\n有無巴絲打教路？謝謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1185821183f674e5a2685fc301a291eb3ee1f765","tid":2079113,"uid":132488,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T14:40:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g3Yo322.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg3Yo322.jpg&h=200897dc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5999030bd02e3e6f3f0b7fef0ff15c6ea8f05659","tid":2079113,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1185821183f674e5a2685fc301a291eb3ee1f765","tid":2079113,"uid":132488,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T14:40:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g3Yo322.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg3Yo322.jpg&h=200897dc&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T14:41:24.000Z","msg":"人哋未借啊<br />\n出錯圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc53770ac78baa31c62384f948b774b01147fa00","tid":2079113,"uid":653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T14:42:03.000Z","msg":"無錢學咩人讀書 仲要有正職<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 